<head>
    <title>Thank You</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/webp" href="https://cdn.discordapp.com/emojis/1305358610154393750.webp?size=1024">
    <!-- <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script> -->
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,opsz,wght@0,14..32,100..900;1,14..32,100..900&family=VT323&display=swap');
        /*
        * CORE SETUP: Ensure full viewport height
        */
        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f4f8; 
        }

        /*
        * BODY CENTERING & BACKGROUND IMAGE LOGIC
        * The flex settings center the content-box AND the copyright text as a group.
        */
        body {
            /* Flexbox Centering */
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; /* Stack items vertically (box and copyright) */
            justify-content: center; /* Center group vertically */
            align-items: center; /* Center group horizontally */
            min-height: 100vh; 

            /* Custom Background Image */
            background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/66274/sunset-poppy-backlight-66274.jpeg?cs=srgb&dl=pexels-pixabay-66274.jpg&fm=jpg');
            background-size: cover;       /* makes it fill the screen */
            background-repeat: no-repeat; /* no tiling */
            background-attachment: fixed; /* stays still when you scroll */
            background-position: center;  /* keeps it centered */
            background-color: transparent; 
        }

        /*
        * STYLING FOR THE CONTENT BOX
        */
        .content-box {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2); /* Made more transparent to reveal blur */
            padding: 40px 60px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 90%; 
            width: 450px; 
            margin: 0;

            /* !!! NEW: Add backdrop-filter for blur effect !!! */
            backdrop-filter: blur(8px); /* Adjust blur value as needed */
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px); /* For Safari support */
        }

        /* --- HEADING SIZES --- */
        h1 {
            font-size: 2.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem; /* Increased margin for better spacing */
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        
        /* Subheading styling */
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 1.5rem; /* Added top margin to separate from the table/paragraphs */
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #1f2937;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem; 
            color: #1f2937; 
            margin-bottom: 1rem; /* Added margin to separate paragraphs */
        }

        /* --- TABLE STYLING --- */
        .table-container {
            width: 100%;
            table-layout: fixed; 
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .table-container td {
            padding: 15px 5px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); 
        }

        .table-container img {
            display: block;
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto; 
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            border-radius: 5px; 
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="content-box">
        <h1>Lest We Forget</h1><br>
        <p>I have paused access to this site, to remember the people we lost during WWI & WWII</p>
        <p>On November 11th 1918, WWI came to a halt. That day is now known as Remembrance Day.</p><br>
        <h2>Heroes never truly die, they just live on in the freedom they fought for.</h2><br>
        <table class="table-container">
            <tr>
                <td><img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/emojis/1305358610154393750.webp?size=64" alt="Emoji" style="height: 64px;"></td>
                <td><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d9/Flag_of_Canada_%28Pantone%29.svg" alt="Flag of Canada" style="height: 56px;"></td>
                <td><img src="https://colebohte.github.io/cb.png" alt="CB Logo" style="height: 64px;"></td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
    <p style="color: white;">Copyright Â© Cole Bohte, River Games, C0LEsGaMinG Games 2022-2025</p>
</body>
